long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
‚ú® Hustle is a very delicate new tab extension that we created for users who enjoy modern simplicity. 

In a nutshell - it's a new tab browser extension composed of a few simple but practical features. Please note that the use of the search feature within the new tab extension will be powered by Microsoft Bing. 

The design of your new tab will look completely different, something you will get used to very quickly, and it will stimulate all your senses needed to get your tasks done - meaning, it can work as a form of motivation. 

Others can find it just suitable for their new tab look - with the classy design and discreet properties, Hustle is the perfect decorating tool for your browser. 

We will list all the essential features Hustle contains, but the rest are more or less valuable options hidden in the new tab:
    - You will get an indistinct search bar that matches your new browser habitat.
    - Shortcuts under the search bar also match the environment. 
    - Shortcuts include bookmarks, to-do list, notes, history, extension settings, 
       youtube, booking, amazon, and many other fun and useful attributes.

There are also ten different background images with a 'rich lifestyle' theme, and a few 'corner' options that allow you to customize your new tab (you can't make significant changes, but if you decide you don't want some features, you can turn them off).

That is all we could say about Hustle extension, if you want more information, visit these pages on our website:
